Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Straw Hat and Desire \Nfell into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Avelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. I'll take \Ncare of them as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DEPARTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
